Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.01,Dialogue,Credits,0,0,0,,Subtitle-source: Detective Conan - 254 [Kaizou][6FC400C1].avi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:06.06,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(167.009,402.6)}Song by Miki Matsuhashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.31,0:00:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hint to reasoning is to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a mystery behind every case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the fate of these two officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will the other half make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:17.99,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,Something's just not right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:17.99,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Something's just not right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.16,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,nani o motometeru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.16,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,What are you aiming for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:26.92,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,uso ni narete yuku kyou mo fake your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:26.92,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I'm now used to your lies, and your eyes are fake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.84,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,The start of century
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.84,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,The start of century.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:36.80,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,tashika na mono nakute
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:36.80,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Nothing's for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:41.64,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,hitori ja nakenai yowasa hate myself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:41.64,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I can't cry alone and I'm weak, I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:51.48,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,shinjiteru itami hikikae ni kono mune umetsukushite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:51.48,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I've buried my heart in exchange for the pain of believing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:01:00.33,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,ima utsutte iru futari ga eranda michi kuru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:01:00.33,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,The future that's reflecting our choices is coming near.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.66,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.66,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I think it's only my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:07.17,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,hateshinai yami no mukou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:07.17,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Beyond the infinite darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:13.80,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,dare mo shiru koto no nai ashita ga aru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:13.80,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,There's an unknown tomorrow awaiting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:18.43,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,oh yeah, You're going nowhere, It's only destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:18.43,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you're going nowhere, it's only destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:21.56,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,ari no mama ni susunde
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:21.56,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Keep moving as you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:29.23,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,ima kanjite iru you're in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:29.23,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I can feel you now, you're in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:32.73,Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,You're in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:32.73,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,You're in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing about Officer Sato from Yumi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found out Officer Sato had agreed\Nto a marriage arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's alright. We've arranged for a way\Nto save her from the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:01.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, who's going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, that'll be Takagi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll send him a message telling him to save her from the\Nmeeting place by making up an emergency case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun will definitely go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we all decided to go check on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Shiratori... The officer...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's with Sato-san now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that means Officer Sato's meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Shiratori!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Robber!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, Officer Takagi took up the robbery case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After watching the criminal enter the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They found three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they had a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's stories were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it'll only be a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, is this Yumi-san? I'm busy with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun asked a favor of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd Conan-kun ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, please try to understand the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By checking your mail immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only mail I've received today\Nis what Yumi-san sent earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Miwako is having a marriage arrangement..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SATO-SAN IS WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you had seen it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's alright, calm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still have some time before sunset, and the\Narrangement is only taking place in Haido City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What about sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Sato only agreed to the arrangement with one condition:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Officer Takagi solved his case and\Nshowed up before sunset for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't accept the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, tell me all about the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heeey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:26.49,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(318.998,121)}The Metropolitan Police Detective Love Story 4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:26.49,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(309.984,344)}(Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Metropolitan Police Detective Love Story 4, Part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've determined that the criminal responsible for\Nthis case is one of these three from the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those three are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.38,Top,,0,0,0,,First is Zama Hiroshi-san, age 21. Freelancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:44.34,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(321.002,351)}Zama Hiroshi (21)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:44.34,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.992,466)}Freelancer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:46.80,Top,,0,0,0,,He is wearing a blue sweatshirt at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:52.77,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(318.998,353)}Kamieda Yusuo (32)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:52.77,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.992,469)}School Coach
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:54.10,Top,,0,0,0,,The next one is Kamieda Yusuo-san, age 32.\NHe said he is a school coach at a local school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's wearing a green sweater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:04.24,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(303.975,348)}Koshimizu Eiko (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:04.24,Dialogue,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(301.972,465)}Office Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:02.86,Top,,0,0,0,,The last one is Koshimizu Eiko-san, age 28, an O.L.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:08.24,Top,,0,0,0,,She's wearing a black shirt with a purple top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the criminal did this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was wearing a helmet and coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was holding a sign that demanded\Nthe owner surrender the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, we followed him to the toilet and found his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was an old man that saw him up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old man said the robber was a woman with a blue shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a girl in a shop that saw the criminal from a shop\Nwindow, and said he was wearing a green shirt under his coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the restaurant manager said the\Nsuspect was wearing a black shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girl said it was a male of about 180cm,\Nbut we're not sure about the shirt's color.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's description of the criminal is different, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't fun, Kudo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's begin with the restaurant master Mamehara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know the master's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know him well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Officer! What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you catch the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take the master outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can talk inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, just wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your glasses turned into sunglasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:07:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The master's glasses are likely the type that take 15 seconds\Nto tint themselves after being exposed to UV light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just remembered that the master\NI know doesn't even wear glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I forgot about the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only started wearing them because it's today's fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then is it possible that when you saw the robber your tinted\Nglasses changed whatever the color was to black?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I'm sure the robber was about 170cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But a girl that saw the robber claimed he was at least 180cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From which store did she see the robber?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was from a clothing store about\None-hundred meters from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that store...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you go there now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl said the robber's head was\Nsticking out from the crowd, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sidewalk leads from the subway exit to the bus stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It often gets rather crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If other people were walking toward you,\Nhow would you walk, Officer Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I would avoid running into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if that slows your pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would get off of the sidewalk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And walk on the curb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the criminal was running on the curb,\Nshe would think he was 180cm tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a jigsaw puzzle, Officer Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes if a piece doesn't fit at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can change the angle and make it fit perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be sure to remember that their testimonies\Nare crucial to completing the puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And showing us the true face of our criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun is taking awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go check on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Conan-kun eat something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For breakfast we had eggs and toast...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? It wasn't the person you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next is the old man that ran into the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my reasoning is correct, he has the key to this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why... Why are you helping me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure you talk to the old man again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you'll know who the criminal is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, w-wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, the old man said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the robber was a woman with a blue shirt under her coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the only one in blue is Zama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, it's the piercing. He thought Zama-san\Nwas a woman because of his piercing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the robber was wearing a helmet at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He couldn't have seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, there's only forty minutes until\Nsunset. If I don't hurry, Sato-san will...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! I see it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand! I understand who the criminal is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's getting darker out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato-san, it isn't that I don't trust you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if Takagi-kun doesn't show, I'll need a confirming kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kiss of engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean us, Shiratori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Takagi-kun doesn't show, we'll be getting married anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you did give your word, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's taking so long, Takagi-kun?\NHurry and capture that criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Takagi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you discover anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing. The three testimonies still don't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A woman with a blue shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man with a green shirt that's 180cm tall...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A person in black that's about 170cm tall...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Based on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't pick out just one of these three as the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can relax. It's still just before 15:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your watch must be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's past 16:30...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The restaurant master said he saw a black\Nundershirt through his tinted glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the girl said 180cm because she saw\Nthe robber running on the curb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you take black clothing and 180cm away,\Nwhat we know about the robber is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a man of 170cm wearing green.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Kamieda-san, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the old man that was knocked down\Nsaid it was a woman in blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, but we forgot to take into account that he is elderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look outside, Miwako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sunset is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have about thirty minutes to sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:13:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takaaggiiiiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! He's elderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It makes sense for him to call green "blue."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, indigo, aqua, green...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They all used to be called green, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hit me when I remembered you were a school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you don't want your students to determine the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wear your watch on the inside of your wrist,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So only you can tell time in class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old man thought the robber was a woman\Nbecause he saw the watch like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:15:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, after becoming tired of changing it before and after class,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He decided to always wear it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means, after considering all three testimonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only one that could be the robber, Kamieda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only ten minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I win then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't look so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get married right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to give you all the time you need to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll always be at your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiratori-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A call?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sato-san? It's Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've just captured the robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The restaurant you're at is five minutes\Nfrom here so I think I can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What has taken you so long!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, can I ask you something before I come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you pick me to come and rescue you from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just thought you'd come, is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm... Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That Sato-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the? The criminal is getting away!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Takagi-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, but... The time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's either me, or the robber...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go, Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright with that? He won't make it if he goes after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is our fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be my fault for making this deal simply\Nbecause of my trust in Takagi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But a deal's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspect arrested at 16:46.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The money, it was for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For my divorce...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I needed money for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:17:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm too far away now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the Minatorou restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's of no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did it, Takagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I've lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That thing I wanted the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it? Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just do it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O.K.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Miwako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take time to clear your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:19:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no longer a wall between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we go, here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Araide-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-san, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you an officer? Then act like an officer\Nand don't give up until the time is up, Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the sun has almost set.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How important he has become to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To realize this so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm no officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's time to stop being one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye bye, Takagi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secondary Inspector Sato Miwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for disturbing you on\Nyour day off, but there's a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your help is needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Takagi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came, Officer Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess it isn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun! Huh? Takagi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi ran toward the exit just then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, what's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miwako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss?
