Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:32.53,Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Tsuyoi chikara de Kimi ni dakare Tobidashitai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm late, the sun has completely set...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:22:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sergeant Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Hurry and get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sato-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looking at their developing romance...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reminds me of someone and someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do feel sorry for Inspector Shiratori, though.
